{"tid":1896703,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃音樂人 人山人海亞里安 過左身","createTime":"2020-02-25T09:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T12:15:44.000Z","uid":34047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc5850eb3ec173adfebbdfe887b6c4ffabee770","tid":1896703,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E6%A2%85%E8%89%B7%E8%8A%B3-%E9%99%B3%E7%8F%8A%E5%A6%AE%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%9E%E9%87%8C%E5%AE%89%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B4-52-%E6%AD%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25A2%2585%25E8%2589%25B7%25E8%258A%25B3-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%258F%258A%25E5%25A6%25AE%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%259E%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25B9%25B4-52-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=89f24d96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25A2%2585%25E8%2589%25B7%25E8%258A%25B3-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%258F%258A%25E5%25A6%25AE%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%259E%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25B9%25B4-52-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&h=1def273e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E6%A2%85%E8%89%B7%E8%8A%B3-%E9%99%B3%E7%8F%8A%E5%A6%AE%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%9E%E9%87%8C%E5%AE%89%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B4-52-%E6%AD%B2/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港知名音樂人、「人山人海」成員亞里安（Arion）昨晚逝世，終年52歲。相識三十多年的好友袁智聰今日在Facebook公布亞里安逝世消息，幾代港人紛感惋惜。<br />\n<br />\n本地樂評人袁智聰今日在Facebook專頁發文悼念亞里安，寫道：「相識30多年的知心好友亞里安在昨晚離世，令人難以接受」。袁智聰憶述與亞里安有很多共同音樂喜好，合作多年，曾一起主持電台節目、籌辦演出、寫歌等。袁智聰說：「我們都是這樣長大的」。他形容亞里安是「很念舊很重情義的朋友」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/YaLiAnArionAuYeung/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2FYaLiAnArionAuYeung%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=671d20d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/YaLiAnArionAuYeung/</a>"},{"pid":"8f95cbc6873ec782d75d69bc5cc10afef7d92c1d","tid":1896703,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:49:11.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5869588e9215fbe63b2299a03e6b66a312d8c5","tid":1896703,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:50:18.000Z","msg":"佢fb可以睇到佢立埋"},{"pid":"87d4e39c0077c1684c518041366591eeb9d55a5f","tid":1896703,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c5869588e9215fbe63b2299a03e6b66a312d8c5","tid":1896703,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:50:18.000Z","msg":"佢fb可以睇到佢立埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"立場"},{"pid":"38dfa6a1016f995b8df3297021fe3e3415d12149","tid":1896703,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b147d24f739d11b3d3f26da784ff01c79461a976","tid":1896703,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"關勁松亞里安嗰個亞里安？"},{"pid":"cd7b56e21b1f6bb1c9e828221efa5a5bfbc393cc","tid":1896703,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b147d24f739d11b3d3f26da784ff01c79461a976","tid":1896703,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"